Title: Object: A landscape of Claude Lorrain with the flight into Egypt
Description: Landscape with flight into Egypt; at left, St Joseph leading a donkey carrying the Virgin and Christ Child towards the right; at right, a peasant and two cows crossing a wooden bridge; a flock in the distance, at centre. 1757 Etching and engraving
Acquisition name: Bequeathed by: Clayton Mordaunt Cracherode (with Philipe's blindstamp and initials CMC)
